		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</p><p><em>This packet holds 1d6 + 4 pinches of dust that condense water into a marble-sized pellet or desiccate watery creatures.</em></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 15 ft Cube (Touch)</p><p>Sprinkle a pinch of the dust over water. Up to a 15-foot Cube becomes a marble-sized pellet that floats or rests near where the dust was sprinkled. The pellet weighs next to nothing. Crushing it against a hard surface releases the stored water and destroys the pellet.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 5 ft (Touch)</p><p>Sprinkle a pinch on a Water Elemental or similar creature composed mostly of water within 5 feet of you.</p><p><strong>[[/save CON 13]]{Constitution Save (DC 13)}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 10d6 necrotic]] damage.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Target takes half damage.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Properties</strong></p><ul><li><p>Each pinch of dust is consumed when used.</p></li><li><p>A creature can take a Utilize action to smash a pellet, ending its magic.</p></li><li><p>When first discovered, determine the packet's remaining pinches as 1d6 + 4.</p></li></ul><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-sKauzfT7TYNuqK0B\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Determine Number of Pinches</strong> activity consumes item uses to set a total of 1d6 + 4 remaining uses. After you establish the count, you may delete that activity.</p></section>",
